Steps to be completed in the terminal for all three (React, RESTAPI and Table) to be run on different ports - 

^^^^^ For the REST API - complete all steps or copy in paste in the terminal 

cd backend
python -m venv .venv
cp .env.example .env
pip install -r requirements.txt
copy .env.example .env
python init_db.py
python -m uvicorn api_app:app --reload --port 8000

